                  {
                    "value": "This workbook is the official starter dataset for the Power BI Dataviz World Champs - Week 3 Contest. This week’s challenge explores over a century of Olympic history, covering medal outcomes, athlete details, sports, events, and participating nations across both the Summer and Winter Games. Use this longitudinal dataset to uncover patterns, stories, and insights about athletic achievement, national performance, gender representation, era-to-era changes, or anything else you find compelling. We picked this dataset because the Winter Olympics are right around the corner - kicking off on February 6, 2026 - and there’s something magical about exploring 125+ years of Olympic history right as the world gets ready for the next chapter.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI",
                      "fontSize": "12pt"
