                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI",
                      "fontSize": "12pt"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "A dimension table with one row per athlete, including biographical details (birth year, bio text), their first Olympic appearance, total number of Games, and total medals earned. Use this table for athlete‑level stories.",
