                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI",
                      "fontSize": "12pt"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "The central fact table that records event‑level outcomes. Each row represents a single athlete’s result in a single discipline/event, including medal information, country codes, and a link back to both the athlete and the Games.",
